<text id="02-output-contract" title="Tailwind Architecture Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema (draft-07) for the artefact this methodology produces. The validator script enforces required keys plus per-field constraints; forbidden patterns enumerate shapes the agent must never emit.</summary>
  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/tailwind-architecture.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "tailwind_version",
    "token_source",
    "cn_util",
    "extraction_threshold",
    "lint_rules"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "tailwind_version": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": [
        "v3",
        "v4"
      ]
    },
    "token_source": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "cn_util": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "path",
        "uses_tailwind_merge"
      ]
    },
    "extraction_threshold": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "min_utilities",
        "min_call_sites"
      ]
    },
    "lint_rules": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "dark_mode_strategy": {
      "type": "string",
      "enum": [
        "semantic_tokens",
        "concrete_shades"
      ]
    }
  }
}
]]></code>
  </section>
  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "tailwind_version": "v3",
  "token_source": "tailwind.config.ts",
  "cn_util": {
    "path": "src/lib/utils.ts",
    "uses_tailwind_merge": true
  },
  "extraction_threshold": {
    "min_utilities": 5,
    "min_call_sites": 3
  },
  "lint_rules": [
    "no-arbitrary-values",
    "no-raw-clsx",
    "prettier-plugin-tailwindcss"
  ],
  "dark_mode_strategy": "semantic_tokens"
}
]]></code>
  </example>
  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "tailwind_version": "v5",
  "token_source": "",
  "cn_util": {
    "path": "src/lib/utils.ts"
  },
  "extraction_threshold": {
    "min_utilities": 1,
    "min_call_sites": 1
  },
  "lint_rules": [],
  "dark_mode_strategy": "concrete_shades"
}
]]></code>
    <note>tailwind_version not in enum; token_source empty; cn_util missing uses_tailwind_merge; extraction_threshold too low; lint_rules empty; dark_mode_strategy=concrete_shades forbidden.</note>
  </example>
  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <pattern id="arbitrary-values-creep">Codebase has 600 occurrences of `w-[Npx]` and `bg-[#hex]`; rebrand requires grep-replace.</pattern>
      <pattern id="raw-clsx-conflicts">Conditional bg colour ignores override; class string ends with conflicting bg-* and the last in source string wins.</pattern>
      <pattern id="apply-in-component">CSS bundle grew 40% after a feature; JIT tree-shaking ineffective.</pattern>
    </list>
  </section>
  <reference path="scripts/validate-tailwind-architecture.py">Validator script (see scripts/).</reference>
</text>
